description         \
    Yet another cross-platform graphical process/system monitor

long_description    \
    {*}${description}, with a customizable interface and a multitude of \
    features. Supports Linux, macOS, and Windows. Inspired by gtop, gotop, \
    and htop.

categories          sysutils
